lyrics:
1. Un duto joma dak e piny,
Weruru Ruoth gi duol maber;
Tiurune, pakuru En;
Biuru nyime kendo umor.

2. Nyasaye, ung'e, ni Ruoth maduong'
En kende ma nochweyowa:
Wan kwedhene, okwayowa;
Oyiewa ka rombege.

3. Donjuru ode to gi pak;
Suduru ire ka umor:
Pakuru Nyinge, miye duong',
Timo kamano owinjowa.

4. Paruru ka Nyasaye ober;
Ndalo duto En ong'uon;
To nene chon owach adier,
To ok onyalo lokore.

5. Ber ji gi jomalaika
Gipake to gi miye duong',
Nyasachwia, Wuonwa me Polo,
Gi Wuode kod Roho Maler.

1. Kama Jawar nothona e Yath,
Luok mar richo duto nitie;
Rembe onyal los chunyi mapoth
Nyinge ni duong'.

Chorus:
Nyinge ni duong'!
Nyinge ni duong'!
Rembe noluoko chunya maler;
Nyinge ni duong'!

2. Kuom warruok maduong' kama!
Yesu okelo hawi kuoma;
Nothona e Yath, nogayoa;
Nyinge ni duong'!

3. Soko ma nochwer mowaroa,
Omiya mor kasedonjoe;
Yesu owara, oritoa;
Nyinge ni duong'!

4. Biuru e Soko machwernu;
Keturu chunyu kuom Jawaru:
Yieuru koro noluoku;
Nyinge ni duong'!

1. Neuru Ruoth mar Ruodhi kobiro giduong';
Wakulre mond' walame kuom tich mabeyo duto.
Ogolo joge e richo oriembo wasigu;

Chorus:
Wapak, Wapakuru Emmanuel, Wapak Emmanuel.
Wami nyinge puoch nyaka chieng' kuom ng'wonone maduong'
Herane mondo odag odagi e chunywa,
En e Wuowi ma miderma mowaro piny duto;
Wapak, Wapakuru Emmanuel, Wapak Emmanuel.

2. Mana kaka apaka gingore e nam;
E machal kod wende mawa pako go herane.
Ogolo joge e chandruok ogonyo jomo motwe;

3. Nobedie mor maduong' kuom jomaler mag Ruoth;
Kawana nene kobedo e kom duong'ne mar loch.
Waduto wanawer gi mor kawa dendo nyinge;

1. In Maler adiera! Wuonwa Nyakalaga!
Koro ka gokinyi wawer ka wapakoi;
In Maler adiera! In manyalo duto!
Wuonwa gi Wuode kod Roho Maler!

2. In Maler adiera! jo maler gilami,
Nyaka nene jogi nopakoi ka gimor;
Kendo Malaika gin mopaki chutho,
In nyaka nene, koro nyaka chieng'.

3. In Maler adiera! Wuonwa Nyakalaga!
Onge jo maricho maneno duong'ni kuno;
In Maler, In kendi; onge moro kodi;
Maduong' mwahero, In Maler adier.

4. In Maler adiera! Wuonwa Nyakalaga!
Tichni duto ma ni e piny gi nam gi Polo;
Duto biro paki, In mang'won manyalo;
Wuonwa gi Wuode kod Roho Maler.

1. An adwaro Yesu maloyo fedha;
Bedo ng'ate oloyo mwandu mathoth,
En ma nothona orita maber;
Adwaro bet gi Yesu moloyo;

Chorus:
Kata abedo Ruodh pinje mathoth
Kendo richo notweya;
Bedo gi Yesu oloyo duto
Ma pinyini dimiya.

2. Bedo gi Yesu oloyo pak mar ji;
Naluwe gadieri kendo tiyone,
Yesu oloyo yudo nying maduong',
Adwaro bet gi Yesu moloyo.

3. Yesu ober maloyo gik ma ni e piny,
Omitna ahinya maloyo mor kich,
Orom' chunya pile ok nachandi;
Adwaro bet gi Yesu moloyo.

1. Daheri moloyo, Yesu Kristo,
Ma to e lamona kaluoroi;

Chorus:
Winja e lamona, Miya chuny mar heri,
Heri adier, Ruodha Yesu.

2. Nadwaro mor me piny, Ber kod yu weyo;
Koro ayieni tim dwaroni.

3. Or gi mineno ber, Tuo gi sand;
Gi manyalo yuwaya kuomi pile.

4. Nyaka naa e piny, Pod apaki;
Naheri moloyo ndalo duto.

1. Keduru jo ka Yesu, jokedo mar Kristo;
Keluru kuodi mau, makuru tong' gi luth.
Yesu Jageng'a marwa, otelonwa maber;
Weuru duto luoro, keduru ka mager.

2. Keduru jo ka Yesu, wasigu mawa kwiny;
To Yesu en kokonywa wanyalo loyo en;
Satani en wasigu ma dwaro negowa;
Kwaluwo bang' Ruoth Yesu wabiro hewoe.

3. Keduru jo ka Yesu, ndalo odong' matin;
Tinende wadhi kedo, kiny wadhi weyo lueny.
Mohewo e moyudo i Polo mor mathoth,
To nyaka chieng' e Polo wasiki kodi Ruoth.

1. Ende wadhiuruwa, wan joluenj Kristo,
Msalap Ruoth Yesu e modhi nyimwa.
Ruodhwa e motelonwa ni wasikwa ka;
Ende wadhiuru tinde, wan joluenj Kristo.

Chorus:
Ende wadhiuruwa,
Wan joluenj Kristo,
Msalap Ruoth Yesu
E modhi nyimwa.

2. Ka jo-Kristo timo chir, jo-Satani a;
Wanalo wasigu, ka waikore.
To wapak Jatelowa, mi wamor adier;
Wan jolueny mageno Yesu, e momiwa mor.

3. Wan oganda Ruoth Yesu, Joge maradier;
To jo-Kristo duto gin owetewa;
Ee, wawuotho kaachiel, ok wapogore;
Wan achiel kuom geno, hera, tim maler duto.

4. Kata pinje lokore, duong' mar piny olal,
To Kanisa Yesu chuweyo nyaka chieng';
Tho gi liel ok nyale ngang' Luanda mar Yesu;
Ende wadhiuru tinde, wan joluenj Kristo.
